column2: SELECT s.specObjID, p.class, p.subClass, x.z, x.ra, x.dec, x.plate, x.fiberID, x.MJD, s.oii_#_flux as OII3#, s.oiii_#_flux as OIII4#,s.oiii_#_flux as OIII5#, s.h_beta_flux as HBeta,s.h_alpha_flux as HAlpha,s.nii_#_flux as NII6#,x.logMass as logM FROM galSpecLine s JOIN stellarMassFSPSGranEarlyDust x ON x.specObjID = s.specObjID JOIN galSpecInfo p ON p.specObjID = s.specObjID WHERE x.plate = # AND x.fiberID = #
